HEADWORD: Theomachist
<hw>The*om"a*chist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. Gr.
<?/.]</ety> <def>One who fights against the gods; one who resists God of
the divine will.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

